          "type": "section_heading",
          "section_suffix": "1.1",
          "text": "菌液制备：",
          "bold": true,
          "section_ref": "detection"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "取大肠埃希菌新鲜培养物（1白金耳）至"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "field_key": "layout/microbiology/ecoli/tsb_volume",
          "underline": true,
          "initial_chars": 3,
          "placeholder": "10",
          "default": "10"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "ml 胰酪大豆胨液体培养基中，在"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "field_key": "layout/microbiology/ecoli/tsb_temperature",
          "underline": true,
          "initial_chars": 5,
          "placeholder": "30～35",
          "recommended_range": {
            "min": 30,
            "max": 35
          },
          "default": "35"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "℃培养"
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "field_key": "layout/microbiology/ecoli/tsb_hours",
          "underline": true,
          "initial_chars": 5,
          "placeholder": "18～24",
          "recommended_range": {
            "min": 18,
            "max": 24
          },
          "default": "18"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "h，作为菌液"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "。吸取上述菌液"
        },
